simulator.elevatorcontrol

Class DriveCommandCanPayloadTranslator

  • java.lang.Object
    • simulator.payloads.translators.CanPayloadTranslator
      • simulator.elevatorcontrol.DriveCommandCanPayloadTranslator

  • public class DriveCommandCanPayloadTranslator
extends CanPayloadTranslator
    Can payload translator for the drive command, which includes a speed value and a direction. See the documentation for DesiredFloorCanPayloadTranslator for more discussion on CanPayloadTranslators in general.
